      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tur eezehele wiꞥsch teem\nLaudim) weenu Likkunin un\neeſu/un tur pahrbaudija wiꞥsch\nohs/ un fazzija: Ja juhs tiffu-\nhti klausifeet ta KUNGA juhsu\nDeewa Balkini/ un darrifeet/\nas teefa irr winna Azzis/ un lik-\net winna Banslus wehrā/ un\nrgafeet wiſus winna Likku-\nnus/ tad ne likschu es par juhs\ne kahdu Wahjibu/ ko es pahr\ngiptes-Semmi lizzis eſmu / jo\ns efimu tas KUNGS taws\nhrste."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Eelim atkaž aisgah-\njuſchi/ nahze wiſfa Israēta Behr-\nnu Draudse us to Tukfnesi Sin/\nkas starp Eelim un starp Sinai\nirr/ peektā padeſinitā Deenā/ oh-\ntrā Mehnefi/ pehz winan Jece-\nfchanas no Egiptes-Semmes."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſfa Israēta Behrnu\nDraudse kurneja prett Mohsu un\nAāronu Tukfnefi."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israēta Behrni fazzija\nus teem : Kaut mehs Egiptes-\nSemmē buhtum nomirruschi\nzaur ta KUNGA Rohku / kad\nmehs pee teem Gattas Bohdeem\nfehdejam/ kad mums Maisē pa-\npillam bij ja-ehd/ jo tu eſti nuhs\nus fcho tukfchu Weetu isweddīs/\nfcho wiſfu Draudsibu zaur Bad-\ndu mehrdeht."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\nus Mohsu : Reds/ es likschu\njuns Maisi no Debbes liht / un\nteem Laudim buhs iſeet / un fa-\nlaſſibt ikdeen as fatvu Mehrn/\ntadeht ka es tohs pahrbandn/ ar\ntee mannā Bauslibā staiga /\njeb ne?"
